International Soccer Tournament (Toronto) 2006


Organized by CPSL and Jornal Desportivo (Portuguese newspaper in Toronto)
Matches at Lamport Stadium

12 May 2006
Santa Clara - Serbian White Eagles   2-1
SC Braga - Toronto Supra             5-0 

14 May 2006
Toronto Supra - Serbian White Eagles 1-1 (pen 6-5)
  Alex Posada 59; Sasa Vicikmez 36

Final
Braga - Santa Clara                  0-0 (pen 4-2) 

att: 850
